2.5, 773.2, 1112.4, 794.1]}, {"text": "expected to vest through May 2010. All DSUs vest upon fulfilling service conditions or upon a director’s", "bbox": [162.5, 798.2, 1112.2, 819.1]}, {"text": "departure from the Board under the terms of the Policy. The total fair value of DSUs that vested during the years", "bbox": [162.5, 823.2, 1112.4, 844.1]}, {"text": "ended December 31, 2007 and 2006 was $0.9 million and $1.2 million, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 848.2, 867.3, 869.1]}, {"text": "Restricted Stock Units", "bbox": [162.5, 914.9, 352.6, 935.7]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the different types of restricted stock units (“RSUs”) granted by the", "bbox": [204.2, 954.1, 1112.4, 974.9]}, {"text": "Company (in thousands):", "bbox": [162.5, 979.1, 373.3, 999.9]}, {"text": "For the Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [869.0, 1026.7, 1112.5, 1043.3]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [885.9, 1051.7, 919.3, 1068.3]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [974.1, 1051.7, 1007.4, 1068.3]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [1062.2, 1051.7, 1095.5, 1068.3]}, {"text": "RSUs with service-based vesting conditions . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1082.0, 848.1, 1102.8]}, {"text": "1,529", "bbox": [879.2, 1082.0, 926.0, 1102.8]}, {"text": "588", "bbox": [982.9, 1082.0, 1014.2, 1102.8]}, {"text": "834", "bbox": [1071.0, 1082.0, 1102.3, 1102.8]}, {"text": "RSUs with performance-based vesting conditions . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1107.0, 848.1, 1127.8]}, {"text": "898", "bbox": [894.8, 1107.0, 926.0, 1127.8]}, {"text": "1,409", "bbox": [967.3, 1107.0, 1014.2, 1127.8]}, {"text": "2,412", "bbox": [1055.4, 1107.0, 1102.3, 1127.8]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1140.3, 848.1, 1161.2]}, {"text": "2,427", "bbox": [879.2, 1140.3, 926.0, 1161.2]}, {"text": "1,997", "bbox": [967.3, 1140.3, 1014.2, 1161.2]}, {"text": "3,246", "bbox": [1055.4, 1140.3, 1102.3, 1161.2]}, {"text": "Each RSU represents the right to receive one share of the Company’s common stock upon vesting. The fair", "bbox": [204.2, 1205.7, 1112.4, 1226.6]}, {"text": "value of these RSUs was calculated based upon the Company’s closing stock price on the date of grant, and the", "bbox": [162.5, 1230.7, 1112.4, 1251.6]}, {"text": "stock-based compensation expense is being recognized over the vesting period. Most RSUs with service-based", "bbox": [162.5, 1255.7, 1112.2, 1276.6]}, {"text": "vesting provisions vest in installments over a three- or four-year period following the grant date.", "bbox": [162.5, 1280.7, 966.7, 1301.6]}, {"text": "The Company also granted performance-based RSUs in 2008, 2007 and 2006 to certain employees. These", "bbox": [204.2, 1333.7, 1112.5, 1354.5]}, {"text": "performance-based RSUs will only vest if the Company exceeds specified cumulative revenue and earnings per", "bbox": [162.5, 1358.7, 1112.4, 1379.5]}, {"text": "share targets over a period of three consecutive fiscal years commencing with the year in which the RSU was", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.7, 1112.5, 1404.5]}, {"text": "granted. For performance-based RSUs granted in 2006 and 2007, the maximum number of performance-based", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.7, 1112.1, 1429.5]}, {"text": "RSUs that may vest is equal to 300% of the number of non-performance-based RSUs granted on the same date.", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.7, 1112.4, 1454.5]}, {"text": "90", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}